name: Table Party
summary: Hello players!  Table Party is a party game in which you can compete by playing 13 types of board games and casual games together. Play with your friends& family and enjoy a great and warm time.  Included 🎮10 types of board games: One card, Yacht Dice, Othello, Chess, Checkers, Rummy, Gin Rummy, Yut Nori, Omok, Janggi 🎮3 types of causal games : Stack Up, Flying Arrow, Whack a Mole
